<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-11-0640 </DOCNO><TEXT>The unsatisfactory performance of the heat pump water heaters (air-to-water)in colder ambient temperatures is the main obstacle to the expansionof the residential market for this device. This study examines the possibilityof retrofitting the gas-fired water heater with a heat pump water heater.The result of the investigation on the thermodynamic performance of awater heater system comprised of a heat pump water heater and a gas-firedwater heater is presented in this paper.</TEXT></DOC>